Skip I am an app that keeps an eye on you, I check that you are well through the time of use of your device and your vital signs. I need you to accept the location permissions, access will only be granted when authorised persons check that you are OK. For correct operation I need to stay in the background, so I need you to accept additional permissions. In addition, you must go to Settings -> Applications -> With You and remove battery restrictions. You will have to enter some personal data for your security. They can only be viewed by authorised personnel when they detect little activity on your device and the communication will be secure.
